#subtitle: Paramilitary organizing in defense of the republic.

= Workers' Militias

The *Workers' Militias* are mass organizations for the defense of the Republic against the extremists who threaten it. Some would call them paramilitaries, although currently they are hardly any sort of military. They are officially associated with the pro-democratic parties - the PSOE, the Republican Left, and the Radicals - but by far the largest component is affiliated with the PSOE and the UGT trade union.

[? if workers_psoe < 46 or workers_psoe < workers_falange or workers_psoe < workers_pce : The Workers' Militias are having a more difficult time recruiting, as the PSOE is no longer the dominant party among the workers. Many of their members have left. ?]

